{"tid":195458,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測)猛鬼追魂8 金剛:骷髏島 屍殺列車","createTime":"2017-04-10T15:17:01.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-10T22:11:02.000Z","uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"da42c94e634f0d6f858d2fb6a97f5fcb3dec350d","tid":195458,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T15:17:01.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">睇清楚時間幾點播</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fparadiseangel.wixsite.com%2Fthanksyour%2Fabout1&d=qkncW4ahWQk%2FJA9l97O%2FUjM0pwszV1jUpWwTgNsMWwc%3D&h=6487f9f8\" target=\"_blank\">http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1</a> 按右上主頁可以睇返V台<br />\n<a href=\"http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flive.sk-knower.com%2Fuser%2Fthanksyour%3Flive%3Dvl&d=qkncW4ahWQk%2FJA9l97O%2FUjM0pwszV1jUpWwTgNsMWwc%3D&h=f2b8b461\" target=\"_blank\">http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl</a>可以直接睇到V台<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.vice.cn/contentimage/4160/1424842429v9ebl5jobqt23ox5oxpm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.vice.cn%2Fcontentimage%2F4160%2F1424842429v9ebl5jobqt23ox5oxpm.jpg&h=a6a3bd23&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/7/74/Kong_Skull_Island_Poster.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2F7%2F74%2FKong_Skull_Island_Poster.jpg&h=e6c44758&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/e/e1/Train_to_Busan_Poster.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2Fe%2Fe1%2FTrain_to_Busan_Poster.jpg&h=2f61fae4&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/7/77/John_Wick_Chapter_Two.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2F7%2F77%2FJohn_Wick_Chapter_Two.jpg&h=e56dc0fa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1.這部最新續集故事從五個年青的互聯網游戲者，接到一個神秘的邀請開始，去參加一個名叫《地獄互聯網》站點的特殊聚會，不過他們沒有想到，那是一個恐怖的難以用言語表達的夜晚。 。 。<br />\n<br />\n2.故事設定於1972年，美國發射了人造衛星後，意外在太平洋發現了「骷髏島」。一隊由科學家、軍人及探險家組成的探勘隊伍奉命深入這個從未有人涉足的神秘太平洋島嶼。探勘隊在島上分組行動：一組觀察附近的環境；另一組投下炸彈，以便科學家觀察地殼變動<br />\n<br />\n3.韓國首爾一家證券公司的基金經理人徐碩宇，與妻子分居後因太過專注於工作，疏於照顧自己的女兒秀安。寂寞的秀安希望能在生日當天到釜山探母，碩宇為了答應女兒的生日願望，迫不得已而只好帶女兒，搭上從首爾往釜山的KTX高鐵列車前往。殊不知，一個神秘病毒開始擴散蔓延至整個國家，將感染者全部轉變成了嗜血喪屍，再通過瘋狂咬人傳播至更多的人。政府誤以為這是某種暴動示威而派軍隊阻止..<br />\n<br />\n4.在前殺手約翰&middot;維克殺光維果和約謝夫&middot;塔拉索夫一行人的四天後，約翰開始尋找自己遭到前者搶走的1969年福特野馬，並循跡發現車在維果的弟弟艾倫那裡。約翰在獲得艾倫根據地的門卡後隨即開車前往，並與艾倫的手下們展開飛車追逐及搏鬥，而艾倫也察覺到傳說中「殺神」的到來；在他打倒其手下後，約翰到艾倫的辦公室倒了兩杯酒給他，以示「和平」。接著約翰便開車回家，與自己在殺死維果後帶回家的「沒有取名」狗見面...((TS版))<br />\n<br />\n11 25PM左右播了 隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94e3e5a975896452236211bb9818ee49f2e9523d","tid":195458,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T15:24:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3222aca5c3c97cdfdbe5593d59bff87726a81e2","tid":195458,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T15:39:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13b4a9cfc8c5885b5f3dcc4f70b13fc70d2a0a37","tid":195458,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T17:11:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e29cd1e21fe1ec3b765d5a97c6c10aebc3a63de3","tid":195458,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T18:07:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoj